summary.title: Online banking for legal entities
summary.description:
Online banking for making payments between legal entities.
Opportunities:
- online payments (with a scan of the payment order, signed in the EDI),
- batch payments (xlsx + orders),
- verification of the validity of the signature and the correspondence of the details,
- conducting internal transfers.
